<br>
I got an idea that I think could be fun.  After the raid on Ak'Anon some characters want revenge, others thought their side won.  However not being on a PvP server caused some difficulties.  So I propose the first ever Norrath Battle Royal.  You got two sides, call them Good vs. Bad, Blues vs. Those who don't like the Blues or Heels vs. Babyfaces  But what ever the two side are they meet in the arena.  One character has the power to start the event up, no fighting is allowed before that time, (anyone that punches early should get nuked by everyone).  Once it starts all fight to the last side standing.  That means once your dead your dead, no rezes.  This will have to be on everyone's player honour as well.  Oh...and there is a minimum level you need to be for this event...level one.  This would be a Big Slobberknocker, for anyone to get in on.  No need for GMs or guides, just players having some fun.<br>
<br>
What do you all think?<br>
